1614
02:07:55.250 --> 02:07:56.550
One in five tracer?

1615
02:07:56.630 --> 02:07:58.630
Yep, and tracers point both ways.

1616
02:07:58.710 --> 02:08:02.760
Yeah? Why don't you check
the head space and she should run.

1617
02:08:10.600 --> 02:08:12.810
Upham! Hustle up!

1618
02:08:19.320 --> 02:08:20.940
