1619
02:09:03.150 --> 02:09:04.820
- Corporal Upham?
- Yes, sir.

1620
02:09:04.950 --> 02:09:07.200
We don't have a 30-caliber
machine gun in this position.

1621
02:09:07.280 --> 02:09:10.660
Either Mr. Mellish or Mr. Jackson
in the bell tower needs that.

1622
02:09:10.790 --> 02:09:12.120
Yes, sir.

1623
02:09:12.950 --> 02:09:15.210
Upham! Jackson's fine.
Turn around to Mellish.

1624
02:09:15.290 --> 02:09:16.960
