1646
02:14:44.910 --> 02:14:47.080
Get down! Get down!

1647
02:14:54.130 --> 02:14:57.220
Upham! Upham! 30-cal! Hurry!

1648
02:14:57.300 --> 02:15:00.800
And find the captain!
This flank's going to fold!

1649
02:15:18.740 --> 02:15:20.570
(BULLETS WHIZZING BY)

1650
02:15:37.840 --> 02:15:39.220
(SHOUTING)

1651
02:15:55.690 --> 02:15:58.530
Reversing! He's still in this fight!

1652
02:15:59.530 --> 02:16:02.030
No, no, Ryan, get down! Get down!

1653
02:16:15.000 --> 02:16:16.250
Ryan!

1654
02:16:35.440 --> 02:16:36.860
Ryan!

1655
02:16:39.190 --> 02:16:40.780
- Ryan!
- RYAN: Get off me!

1656
02:16:40.900 --> 02:16:43.360
- Are you all right?
- Get off me!

1657
02:16:43.450 --> 02:16:45.570
Yeah, yeah,
I'm fine, too, Captain. Thanks.

1658
02:16:46.450 --> 02:16:51.000
MILLER: Okay, both sides!
